      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "rationale": "At MRL 3 for a Class II device with moderate model influence, SQA Gradation 2 is required. The FEA software (Abaqus 2023) is used under a validated installation qualification (IQ) and operational qualification (OQ) protocol per 21 CFR Part 11. Version control, regression test suite (847 benchmark cases), and change control procedures are documented in the Software Quality Plan SQP-TKR-2025-001. Achieved Gradation 3 reflects formal IQ/OQ/PQ with documented traceability to ISO 13485 QMS.",
