        "description": "Software must be used under documented IQ/OQ procedures with version control and regression testing. All simulation scripts must be under configuration management. Achieved level must be >= 2. Criterion met: Abaqus 2023 IQ/OQ documented, regression suite passing, scripts in Git repository with tagged release."
      }
    },
