      "rationale": "Code verification at Gradation 2 requires demonstration that the solver correctly implements the mathematical model through benchmark comparisons. Hertz contact analytical solution used to verify FEA contact formulation: FEA peak contact pressure within 2.1% of analytical Hertz solution for a sphere-on-flat benchmark at five load levels. Patch test passed for all element types used. Convergence of iterative solver confirmed with residual tolerance 1e-6.",
      "acceptanceCriteria": {
        "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/ac/nagaraja-cou1-ortho-ac-ncv",
