      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "rationale": "Experimental test conditions documented per ISO 14243-1:2009 protocol. Five cadaveric specimens tested under controlled laboratory conditions: temperature 37°C ± 0.5°C, load application via servo-hydraulic test frame with load cell accuracy ±1% FS, displacement measurement via LVDT ±0.01 mm. Specimen preparation protocol documented with geometric measurements (CT scan, voxel size 0.3 mm). Test conditions mapped to simulation boundary conditions with documented assumptions for fixture stiffness idealization.",
      "acceptanceCriteria": {
