      "rationale": "Nonlinear solver convergence monitored per load increment. Force residual norm < 1e-6 N and displacement correction norm < 1e-8 mm at convergence for all load steps. Contact constraint enforcement via augmented Lagrangian method with penetration tolerance 0.001 mm. Floating point arithmetic errors assessed via double-precision computation and cross-verification with Ansys Mechanical 2024 R1 for two representative load cases — peak contact stress agreement within 0.9%.",
      "acceptanceCriteria": {
