      "rationale": "Model form selection (neo-Hookean hyperelastic for UHMWPE, linear elastic for CoCr tray, frictionless-to-frictional Coulomb contact) justified by published literature and material characterization data. Alternative model forms considered: (1) Mooney-Rivlin hyperelastic — rejected as over-parameterized for available calibration data; (2) elastic-plastic UHMWPE — rejected as strain levels in COU remain below yield. Model form assumptions documented in Model Description Document MDD-TKR-2025-001 with supporting references.",
