      "rationale": "All model inputs documented with sources and uncertainty characterization. UHMWPE material properties (E = 680 ± 55 MPa, ν = 0.46 ± 0.02) from lot-specific tensile testing (n=6 specimens per lot, ASTM D638). CoCr elastic modulus (210 GPa, literature value with ±5% assumed uncertainty). Geometric inputs from CT reconstruction with dimensional verification against CMM measurements (max deviation 0.08 mm). Loading inputs from ISO 14243-1 with ±10% magnitude uncertainty per sensitivity analysis. Achieved Gradation 3 reflects lot-specific material testing rather than literature-only values.",
