        "description": "All primary model inputs must have documented sources and quantified uncertainty. Critical material properties must be derived from experimental testing, not literature alone. Geometric inputs must be verified against physical measurement. Input uncertainty must be propagated through UQ analysis. All criteria met with lot-specific material testing achieving Gradation 3."
